    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"1e8983d1-900e-5568-9b10-b0ea47c8a1b8","excerpt":"zsh プロンプトをカスタマイズする プラグインを入れずにカスタマイズをする。 基本 まず、プロンプトのカスタマイズは.zshrcなどでPROMPT…","html":"<h1>zsh プロンプトをカスタマイズする</h1>\n<p>プラグインを入れずにカスタマイズをする。</p>\n<h2 id=\"基本\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC\" aria-label=\"基本 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>基本</h2>\n<p>まず、プロンプトのカスタマイズは<code>.zshrc</code>などで<code>PROMPT</code>などに値を代入することで行える</p>\n<p>試しに</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># .zshrc</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;$&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/776d3/terminal_%24.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAM0lEQVQY02PQMFD9r6ak+l9dVfW/ugp2rK2h+V9fWwdTTlUNFauo/mdgYGD4T2U8yA0EAOs0WKZaLpykAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"$のみ\"\n        title=\"$のみ\"\n        src=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/f058b/terminal_%24.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/c26ae/terminal_%24.png 158w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/6bdcf/terminal_%24.png 315w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/f058b/terminal_%24.png 630w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/40601/terminal_%24.png 945w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/78612/terminal_%24.png 1260w,\n/static/c987250235266523d660d7cdefbaf81c/776d3/terminal_%24.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>のようになり、またさらに以下のようにすると</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># .zshrc</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;$&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;///&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/776d3/terminal_%24slash.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAMklEQVQY02PQMFD9r6ak+l9dVfW/ugp2rK2h+V9fWwdTTlUNgVUgmIGBgeE/lfEgNxAA6y9YpphYK0IAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"$と///\"\n        title=\"$と///\"\n        src=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/f058b/terminal_%24slash.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/c26ae/terminal_%24slash.png 158w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/6bdcf/terminal_%24slash.png 315w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/f058b/terminal_%24slash.png 630w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/40601/terminal_%24slash.png 945w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/78612/terminal_%24slash.png 1260w,\n/static/bcae8831f66b2526924def85abb24047/776d3/terminal_%24slash.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>となる(左に<code>///</code>が追加された)。</p>\n<h3 id=\"僕のプロンプト\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%83%95%E3%81%AE%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%88\" aria-label=\"僕のプロンプト permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>僕のプロンプト</h3>\n<p>僕はできる限りシンプルにしたかったので、以下のような見た目になっている。\n(普段はこれに tmux を起動して、その他の情報を載せてたりする)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.18987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAUElEQVQI12Ow0Fb8r6aj+F9RTuG/orw8Glb4ryAn/19FSfm/qrIKmA0Sw1QnD1Wn9J9BWELgPy83638GBgaKMRMT038GZhYWqhjGyMgINhAAcDxD+KukyUgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.03.57.png\"\n        title=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.03.57.png\"\n        src=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/c26ae/terminal_my.png 158w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/6bdcf/terminal_my.png 315w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png 630w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/40601/terminal_my.png 945w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/78612/terminal_my.png 1260w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>これの設定ファイルは下に折りたたんだ。この説明は最後で行う。</p>\n<details>\n  <summary>設定ファイル</summary>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">```bash</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">left-prompt() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  local dir=&quot;%F{11}%~%f&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  local next=&quot;%F{47}❯%f &quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  echo -e &quot;\\n${user}${dir}\\n${next}&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">right-prompt() {</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  local time=&quot;%F{242}%T%f&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">  echo &quot;${time}&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">PROMPT=`left-prompt`</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">RPROMPT=`right-prompt`</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">unset -f left-prompt</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">unset -f right-prompt</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\">```</span></span></code></pre>\n</details>\n<h2 id=\"情報の追加\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%83%85%E5%A0%B1%E3%81%AE%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0\" aria-label=\"情報の追加 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>情報の追加</h2>\n<p>現在のディレクトリと時間を表示するためには<code>%~</code>と<code>%T</code>を用いると表示できる。</p>\n<p>例えば</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%~ &gt; &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%T&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると、</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/24def/terminal_info.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15.18987341772152%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAT0lEQVQI162KQQqAMAwEc8g7mrapCJUg+gH//6oRCyKe9TC7A7ty7J2+zcQSNHdyShTLFLPRORmtOpO34c9mr4+XyhqBiMgVqCq3f0T4kxOj90QQYqR2TgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.04.19.png\"\n        title=\"スクリーンショット 2022-04-03 18.04.19.png\"\n        src=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/f058b/terminal_info.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/c26ae/terminal_info.png 158w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/6bdcf/terminal_info.png 315w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/f058b/terminal_info.png 630w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/40601/terminal_info.png 945w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/78612/terminal_info.png 1260w,\n/static/827801fb310f01e0ff4812f5d3e5c2f3/24def/terminal_info.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>のようになる。</p>\n<p>下の表は<a href=\"https://tegetegekibaru.blogspot.com/2012/08/zsh_2.html\">https://tegetegekibaru.blogspot.com/2012/08/zsh_2.html</a>より、そのままコピペさせていただいた。上の例のようにパラメータを<code>PROMPT</code>などに渡せば良い</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>パラメータ</th>\n<th>出力内容</th>\n<th>例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>%M</td>\n<td>ホスト名</td>\n<td>localhost.localdomain</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%m</td>\n<td>ホスト名</td>\n<td>localhost</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%n</td>\n<td>ユーザ名</td>\n<td>root</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%#</td>\n<td>ユーザ種別</td>\n<td>#（root の場合） %（root 以外）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%y</td>\n<td>ログイン端末名</td>\n<td>pts/0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%l</td>\n<td>ログイン端末名</td>\n<td>pst/0（tty*の場合は tty を省略）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%?</td>\n<td>直前のコマンドの戻り値</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%h %!</td>\n<td>コマンド実行数 （history 数）</td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%d %/</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>/root/currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%~</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>~/currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%C</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>currentdir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%c %.</td>\n<td>カレントディレクトリ</td>\n<td>currentdir （$PWD=$HOME の場合は~）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%D</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>12-07-31 (yy-mm-dd)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%W</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>07/31/12 (mm/dd/yy)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%w</td>\n<td>日付</td>\n<td>Sun 31 (day dd)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%*</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>15:50:30 (hh:mm:ss)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%T</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>15:50 (hh:mm)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>%t %@</td>\n<td>時間</td>\n<td>03:50PM (hh:mm(am/pm format))</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"装飾\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A3%85%E9%A3%BE\" aria-label=\"装飾 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>装飾</h2>\n<p>ただの白文字ではつまらないので装飾したい。</p>\n<h3 id=\"色\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"色 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>色</h3>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">%F{色番号}色をつける内容%f</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると色がつけられる。\nつまり<code>%F</code>と<code>%fで</code>囲われたところに色がつく。色はターミナルの 256 色(0~255)で指定する。</p>\n<p>例えば</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{45}%~%f &gt; &quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>とすると</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/776d3/terminal_color.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAASElEQVQY063MOw6AIBQF0Vu84Gcbgr4ABkr3v7GxNdFOilNNMvKrkY5C650zF9IW2WN6iGR36md7k2xGYSIsK2aGpL/EYGOHN1rLWQxIisrAAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"color\"\n        title=\"color\"\n        src=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/f058b/terminal_color.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/c26ae/terminal_color.png 158w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/6bdcf/terminal_color.png 315w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/f058b/terminal_color.png 630w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/40601/terminal_color.png 945w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/78612/terminal_color.png 1260w,\n/static/648baa509a5cdd21ccb5bb1477389577/776d3/terminal_color.png 1814w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>色番号の一覧は次の ruby スクリプトを実行することで見れる。(このスクリプトは数年前にどっかで拾った)</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"ruby\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@fg</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[38;5;&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@bg</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[48;5;&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\x1b</span><span class=\"mtk8\">[0m&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">def</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">code</span><span class=\"mtk1\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  number = </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;%3d&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> % code</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@bg</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">code</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">m </span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">number</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@fg</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">code</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">m </span><span class=\"mtk4\">#{</span><span class=\"mtk1\">number</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}#{</span><span class=\"mtk12\">@rs</span><span class=\"mtk4\">}</span><span class=\"mtk8\"> &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">end</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk7\">256</span><span class=\"mtk1\">.times </span><span class=\"mtk15\">do</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> |</span><span class=\"mtk12\">n</span><span class=\"mtk1\">|</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> color(n)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk15\">if</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> (n + </span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).modulo(</span><span class=\"mtk7\">8</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).zero?</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk15\">end</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">print</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk6\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b85a410e914d68436d6a06c7aff7938c/6ee58/256color.png\"\n    style=\