I12Ow0Fb8r6aj+F9RTuG/orw8Glb4ryAn/19FSfm/qrIKmA0Sw1QnD1Wn9J9BWELgPy83638GBgaKMRMT038GZhYWqhjGyMgINhAAcDxD+KukyUgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"僕の\"\n        title=\"僕の\"\n        src=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/c26ae/terminal_my.png 158w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/6bdcf/terminal_my.png 315w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/f058b/terminal_my.png 630w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/40601/terminal_my.png 945w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/78612/terminal_my.png 1260w,\n/static/aa4388082c8a42f0b46617965fac75a1/24def/terminal_my.png 1812w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"bash\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">left-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> dir=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{11}%~%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> next=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{47}❯%f &quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -e </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${user}${dir}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">\\n</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${next}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">right-prompt</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">local</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> time=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;%F{242}%T%f&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk11\">echo</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk12\">${time}</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">PROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`left-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">RPROMPT=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">`right-prompt`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f left-prompt</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">unset</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> -f right-prompt</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>shell スクリプトで<code>local</code>な関数を設定する方法がわからなかったので最後に<code>unset</code>している。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\" aria-label=\"参考 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><pa